{
  "stem": "12564.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the question was that time, that we know that they will not to let any witnesses, any relatives to survive after the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I decided to go to them for food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were very, very polite, invite me to eat breakfast with them together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were asking where my family is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, we all separate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One doesn't know from the other, in case he gets caught.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But if one will get caught, the families will burn them down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I continue coming to them for months for food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Especially for them to think that we don't know that they did it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they did not look for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was at that time already 13 years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never had.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing what a person in that position was thinking, is how to survive, not to be caught.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the biggest wish was to go to sleep and not to wake up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About every day, you're finding out who else was killed from the people that they were hiding.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the numbers was coming down drastically.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we know all these people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the question was, who was next?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were everyday, was a next person.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they wasn't killed like a rifle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were mostly killed like they're doing in Mexico with hatchets, or the other.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In our area that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Trying to survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not to let yourself to be caught.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Going out in the morning, one day I collected some bread from several people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was too early to go back to our place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I went under a barn, where there were some blocks, staying under the floor, and fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I woke up, I didn't have the bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
